WEBVTT

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:32.680
but they do build
stronger bottom-up support

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:37.216
for policies and solutions that can.

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:40.070
That is why engaging people is so crucial.

00:11:42.120 --> 00:11:44.296
I started this talk

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:47.920
with testing two ways
of communicating climate with you.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:51.656
There is another way, too,

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.000
I'd like to share with you.

00:11:53.800 --> 00:11:56.536
It starts with reimagining climate itself

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:58.320
as the living air.

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:01.976
Climate isn't really
about some abstract, distant climate